subject: Australian Open (Tennis)
Tennis
lead_paragraph: The 19-year-old Sloane Stephens advanced to the semifinals of the Australian Open by rallying to defeat her 31-year-old American elder Serena Williams, 3-6, 7-5, 6-4.
